---
title: Super Quick Cheesy Bacon Orzo with Mushrooms and Rocket
description: Not to be confused with rice, orzo is actually a type of pasta. Super speedy, this Super Quick Cheesy Bacon Orzo is ready in less than 15 minutes, proving it's not always time you need for delicious dinners.
